{"tid":2225634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國動物園5隻鸚鵡爆粗鬧人 被禁接觸遊客","createTime":"2020-10-01T12:51:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T13:19:47.000Z","uid":31744,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e2c4d69c0e6362078743515d5df721cb730e030b","tid":2225634,"uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T12:51:24.000Z","msg":"英國一個野生動物園內有5隻鸚鵡開口「爆粗」咒罵入園的遊客，園方已決定把牠們收起來，不再讓牠們展出及接觸遊人。<br />\n<br />\n那5隻鸚鵡早前獲安排捐給英格蘭東部的林肯郡野生動物園。園方工作人員接收牠們後數天，便發現牠們懂得講粗口，不單只互相對罵，還開口咒罵動物園工作人員和入園遊玩的遊客。5隻鸚鵡屬於非洲灰鸚鵡，牠們分別名為Eric、Jade、Elsie、Tyson和Billy，<br />\n<br />\n動物園行政總裁尼科爾斯接受傳媒訪問時稱「牠們全部懂得罵人，有如連珠炮發。我們有點兒擔心小孩子。每次我步行經過牠們時，都被罵『胖子』」。他指鸚鵡很容易學懂說髒話，而且可以在非常短的時間內學會。尼科爾稱「你想到的，牠們都會說出來。『Fxxk off 』是牠們常說的髒話。」"},{"pid":"05620ddd4f77015b62bcf555b5d15ac978e7ff14","tid":2225634,"uid":228894,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T12:54:43.000Z","msg":"日日播 samuel jackson 啲戲佢地睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9249c7bde920ee2e6b5f890c8a5e6ebb08e5588","tid":2225634,"uid":121580,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T12:56:03.000Z","msg":"互相對罵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ccd00d79644057d1fcf081be84f9e281f7b2db2","tid":2225634,"uid":56807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T12:59:02.000Z","msg":"養返2隻，不斷播電車個段片"},{"pid":"6168d19e6baa694eba78705e3d9c5b31b735c10c","tid":2225634,"uid":281683,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T13:04:34.000Z","msg":"點會收起d鸚鵡，咁先有賣點吸客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efb7d1b1d49a887e888fbaa5c7c756aea90ae32f","tid":2225634,"uid":275370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T13:05:12.000Z","msg":"有冇片<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />